  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct intended for lumbar spinal fusion in adult patients. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories under ASTM F1717 loading. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. Intended use is restricted to static compression-bending QOIs; fatigue and dynamic loading are explicitly out of scope. Regulatory submission target: 510(k) substantial equivalence demonstration for Class II spinal fixation device.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-predicts-f1717-static-cb-performance",
