      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 is a commercially validated solver with documented V&V test suite. FDA in-house FEA code underwent independent code verification per agency SOP. Version control and audit trail maintained for all simulation scripts. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2."
    },
    {
