      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative solver residuals must fall below 1e-6; achieved level must meet required level.",
      "rationale": "Direct sparse solver (PARDISO) used for linear static analysis, eliminating iterative convergence concerns. Residual force norm verified below 1e-8 for all load steps. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
    },
    {
