      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented simulation workflow with peer review; achieved level must meet required level.",
      "rationale": "Simulation workflow documented in a controlled simulation plan reviewed by two independent analysts. Boundary condition application and material assignment verified by a second engineer prior to submission runs. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
