      "acceptanceCriteria": "Multiple test conditions spanning the intended use envelope; achieved level must equal required level 3.",
      "rationale": "Testing conducted at a single load level per ASTM F1717 protocol. Variation in loading angle and offset distance not explored. This factor falls below the required level 3; a risk-informed argument is provided that the single condition represents the worst-case scenario per FDA guidance. Achieved level 2 is below required level 3 — documented deficiency accepted by the assessment team with rationale."
    },
