      "rationale": "Test fixture geometry digitized via CT scan and replicated in FEA boundary conditions. Actuator displacement and load cell placement matched in simulation. Friction coefficients at fixture interfaces measured and applied. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
