      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric applied with uncertainty bounds; achieved level must equal required level 3.",
      "rationale": "Construct stiffness and yield load compared using validation metric (M_val) per ASME V&V 40 Section 5. Mean prediction error 4.2% for stiffness and 6.1% for yield load, both within the 10% acceptance band accounting for experimental uncertainty. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
