      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QOIs directly linked to clinical performance and regulatory submission requirements; achieved level must equal required level 3.",
      "rationale": "Construct stiffness and yield load are the primary QOIs specified in ASTM F1717 and referenced in FDA's spinal system guidance. These QOIs directly inform 510(k) substantial equivalence comparison. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
