      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities conducted under conditions representative of the intended use; achieved level must equal required level 3.",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments replicate the ASTM F1717 test protocol that constitutes the regulatory standard for the intended clinical use. Screw geometry, material, and loading mode in validation experiments are identical to those in the clinical use scenario. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
